org.openqa.selenium.firefox

Class FirefoxOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.firefox.FirefoxOptions

  • public class FirefoxOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Manage firefox specific settings in a way that geckodriver can understand. Use addTo(DesiredCapabilities) to also add settings to a DesiredCapabilities object.

    An example of usage: 

        DesiredCapabilities caps = new FirefoxOptions()
      .addPreference("browser.startup.page", 1)
      .addPreference("browser.startup.homepage", "https://www.google.co.uk")
      .addTo(DesiredCapabilities.firefox());
    WebDriver driver = new FirefoxDriver(caps);
